---
title: Jerk Cauli Nuggets with Protein Loaded Bean Stew
description: Packed with Vitamin C and containing nearly zero grams of fat, sodium or sugar, cauliflower is the hero ingredient in this delicious recipe. Cauliflower ‘nuggets’ are coated with mayo, jerk seasoning and panko breadcrumbs and baked in the oven until golden and crispy. Served with a smokey black bean and spinach stew and finished off with a sprinkling of fresh coriander, it’s a great dish to enjoy for a wholesome mid-week dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jerk-cauli-nuggets-c955dbde-ff834506.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/jerk-cauli-nuggets-5c1bba4ac445fa71dd57ee62-ba4108fc.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 453 kcal
  fat: 17 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
  carbohydrates: 48 g
  sugar: 21 g
  protein: 20 g
  sodium: 4 g
  serving size: 740
